<IMG height=27 hspace=6 src="/images/partners/GD_HighRes.gif" width=140 align=right>The <STRONG>Gaming TechZone</STRONG> offers digital entertainment/gaming companies a place to exhibit, connect and do serious business. Whether your company needs open space for a dynamic, interactive exhibit or a quieter, more intimate venue for scheduled meetings and invitation-only demos, you can create and tailor your presence — and success — at CES. <BR><BR>Gaming buyers attend CES to see gaming hardware and software in concert with the entire range of consumer electronics products. Gaming buyers choose CES to make purchasing decisions — from online PC and HD gaming, plasma HDTV and home theater furniture to surround sound and power conditioning hardware.
