<br><br>

<IMG height=39 src="/images/partners/HDMI_140x39.gif" width=140 align=right><SPAN class=textcolored1><SPAN>High-Definition Multimedia Interface (HDMI) is the acknowledged world standard for connecting HD consumer electronics products and devices. Utilizing only a single, intelligent cable, HDMI provides an all-digital interface that supports all audio and video formats. Users can now connect their home theater system without the mess and hassle of multiple cables and cords while still preserving video and audio quality. <BR><BR>The <STRONG>HDMI TechZone</STRONG> features a sampling of the hundreds of companies that have already adopted this evolutionary technology. Come learn how HDMI can provide consumers and manufacturers with the cutting-edge technology that is needed by visiting one of the newest TechZones at the International CES, the <STRONG>HDMI TechZone</STRONG>.</SPAN></SPAN>
