<br><br>

High Definition Power Line Communication is one of the best power line technologies for the stable transmission of data because of its high performance, speed and HD capacity. With HD-PLC you can create home networks for Internet, high-definition video and audio, camera monitoring, and more, all without extra wiring. Forget about walls between rooms anymore. No need to worry about making holes for wiring, or about walls reducing transmission speed. Simply plug into a wall outlet with your HD-PLC adaptor, and create your home network. 
