<IMG height=39 hspace=6 src="/images/partners/ITS_america.gif" width=200 align=right>Showcase live demos of your automotive warning systems pertinent to traffic and highway management, in-vehicle travel information as well as&nbsp;crash and incident response systems in this one-of-a-kind TechZone. Display the latest technology in active safety systems such as collision warnings, lane departure and curve over-speed, which offer advances in intelligent transportation safety. <BR><BR>This technology showcase welcomes automotive OEMs, ME manufacturers, integrators, navigation developers, location-based services and telematics companies to exhibit. Exhibitors should feature technology for navigation, accident avoidance, connectivity, in-vehicle entertainment and internet and traffic management.<BR><BR><IMG height=35 hspace=10 src="/images/partners/Connexis_120.gif" width=120 align=middle><IMG height=90 hspace=10 src="/images/partners/DOTBW.gif" width=90 align=middle><IMG height=17 hspace=10 src="/images/partners/ECPI_120.gif" width=120 align=middle><IMG height=16 hspace=10 src="/images/partners/TCLogoNoTag.gif" width=140 align=middle>
